flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "E4FC1639428F684669AE2D86E107923B", "Seek and slay! While the Kaelar army and their feeble militia ignore the sacred sites of heroes, we, the Order of Giantslayers do not! Oakenbane Keep has long been a memorial and testament to giant slaying. It is the site of the greatest battle against Aelan and Titan. Oakenbane is now being defiled by the presence of minotaur and their unholy leader, a shaman known as Garumat. Slay the spiritual leader of the minotaur and bring a bit of peace to the giant slayers of the past. - The Order of the Giantslayers")
mainObjectiveText: NSLOCTEXT("", "3F06581B498B8EAE109D4787D2DA645C", "Seek and slay Garumat the Minotaur.")
